node.text:
The question is HOW. How can you be in a completely different place 3 months from now? If you want to learn how, read this short 1 min caption 👇⁣
⁣
The MAIN reason people don’t change is because our brain is designed in a way to keep us safe. Keep us in the KNOWN. Or in other words, our comfort zone. ⁣
⁣
That’s why most children will grow up to have similar economic status to their parents⁣
⁣
Will probably live in the same neighborhood. And will probably hang with the same people they grew up with, simply because they grew up together. Not because they have similar interests, goals, or visions. ⁣

The good thing is - it doesn’t have to apply to YOU. Most people are not everyone. There are people who choose to live differently. Who choose to create success in all areas of their lives. ⁣

How are they doing it? They force their mind to get out of the “familiar and known” and find people who have accomplished what they want to achieve in life.⁣

Simply by surrounding yourself with the right people you can change your life direction. ⁣

That’s why today I highly recommend you follow some of the best mentors on Instagram, I will list them below:⁣
